Given an English text describing an information need, generate a SPARQL query to retrieve relevant data from the DBLP Knowledge Graph using ["<https://dblp.org/pid/93/4824>"] as entities and ["<https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy>", "<https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#yearOfPublication>"] as relations

### Input:
In which year did the author Christopher Z. publish the most research papers?

### Response:
SELECT (GROUP_CONCAT(?answer; separator=', ') AS?answer)?count WHERE { SELECT DISTINCT?answer (COUNT(?answer) AS?count) WHERE {?x <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy> <https://dblp.org/pid/93/4824>.?x <https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#yearOfPublication>?answer } GROUP BY?answer } ORDER BY DESC(?count) LIMIT 1<|end_of_text|>

Given an English text describing an information need, generate a SPARQL query to retrieve relevant data from the DBLP Knowledge Graph using ["<https://dblp.org/pid/87/9169>"] as entities and ["<https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#authoredBy>", "<https://dblp.org/rdf/schema#publishedIn>"] as relations

### Input:
